
'''= an open source toolkit for implementing and developing standard methods for calculating normalized metered energy consumption (NMEC) and avoided energy use.'''

URL = http://eemeter.openee.io/

=Description=

"The EEmeter library contains routines for estimating energy efficiency savings at the meter. In particular, it includes the reference implementation of the CalTRACK methods for estimating normalized metered energy savings.

The eemeter is released as open source software under a permissive Apache-2.0 license."


